    println("")
    println("Architecture (v3 - pure hexa):")
    println("  - Evolution via blowup.hexa consciousness domain (no Python)")
    println("  - 5 perspectives: void, emergence, network, boundary, consciousness")
    println("  - Telescope 5-lens verification (blowup Phase 5)")
